"  <div id=\"topicText\">",
"   <p class=\"headingAnchor\" id=\"H1\">",
"    <span class=\"h1\">",
"     CASE 1",
"    </span>",
"    &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;A 36 year-old man presents with fever and chills after a trip to India. What does the thin smear of blood show? Question: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef59913 \" href=\"UTD.htm?42/37/43614\">",
"     picture 1",
"    </a>",
"    ). Answer: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef66536 \" href=\"UTD.htm?0/23/383\">",
"     picture 2",
"    </a>",
"    ).",
"   </p>",
"   <p class=\"headingAnchor\" id=\"H2\">",
"    <span class=\"h1\">",
"     CASE 2",
"    </span>",
"    &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;A 30 year-old man presents with periodic fevers and shaking chills two weeks after a visit to Cameroon. What does the thin smear of blood show? Question: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef82243 \" href=\"UTD.htm?40/29/41438\">",
"     picture 3",
"    </a>",
"    ). Answer: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef61406 graphicRef72894 \" href=\"UTD.htm?34/22/35171\">",
"     picture 4A-B",
"    </a>",
"    ).",
"   </p>",
"   <p class=\"headingAnchor\" id=\"H3\">",
"    <span class=\"h1\">",
"     CASE 3",
"    </span>",
"    &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;A 45 year-old splenectomized man develops fever and chills three weeks after a trip to the island of Nantucket, off the coast of Cape Cod, Massachusetts. What does the thin smear of blood show? Question: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef52870 \" href=\"UTD.htm?36/2/36910\">",
"     picture 5",
"    </a>",
"    ). Answer: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef59581 \" href=\"UTD.htm?15/11/15536\">",
"     picture 6",
"    </a>",
"    ).",
"   </p>",
"   <p class=\"headingAnchor\" id=\"H4\">",
"    <span class=\"h1\">",
"     CASE 4",
"    </span>",
"    &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;A 52 year-old man has fever and eosinophilia after a trip to Panama. What does the thin smear of blood show? Question: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef72364 \" href=\"UTD.htm?25/25/26014\">",
"     picture 7",
"    </a>",
"    ). Answer: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef50256 \" href=\"UTD.htm?26/19/26942\">",
"     picture 8",
"    </a>",
"    ).",
"   </p>",
"   <p class=\"headingAnchor\" id=\"H5\">",
"    <span class=\"h1\">",
"     CASE 5",
"    </span>",
"    &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;A 42 year-old woman from Greece presents with a liver mass. What does the wet mount from the liver lesion show? Question: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef60766 \" href=\"UTD.htm?37/41/38546\">",
"     picture 9",
"    </a>",
"    ). Answer: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef68523 \" href=\"UTD.htm?38/56/39810\">",
"     picture 10",
"    </a>",
"    ).",
"   </p>",
"   <p class=\"headingAnchor\" id=\"H6\">",
"    <span class=\"h1\">",
"     CASE 6",
"    </span>",
"    &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;A 36 year-old man from Brazil presents with cardiac arrhythmias and congestive heart failure. What does the myocardial biopsy show? Question: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_figure graphicRef78714 \" href=\"UTD.htm?0/8/141\">",
"     figure 1",
"    </a>",
"    ). Answer: (",
"    <a class=\"graphic graphic_picture graphicRef59557 \" href=\"UTD.htm?1/18/1312\">",
"     picture 11",
"    </a>",
"    ).",
"   </p>",
