" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Diffuse dorsal swelling of the tenosynovial sheath",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 326px; height: 232px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    This middle-aged office worker presented with acute swelling, pain, and warmth over the back of her hand that was aggravated by typing and other fine finger movements. Swelling involved the index and middle fingers, and proved to be acute dorsal tenosynovitis due to gout. The differential diagnosis also includes reflex sympathetic dystrophy and cellulitis.",
